      <title>哈里斯 7 月募资 3.1 亿美元，在筹款竞赛中超越特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/harris-raises-310-million-in-july-topping-trump-in-money-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯的竞选团队称，她 7 月份筹集的资金达到了创纪录的 3.1 亿美元，使这位民主党预定候选人比共和党人唐纳德·特朗普在资金方面具有优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/harris-raises-310-million-in-july-topping-trump-in-money-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>夏皮罗的敏捷和号召力让他在竞选搭档中占据优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/shapiro-s-agility-and-appeal-give-him-edge-in-running-mate-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗 (Josh Shapiro) 抵达费城参加集会时，全国的阴谋随之而来，费城是美国最重要的摇摆州中最自由的角落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/shapiro-s-agility-and-appeal-give-him-edge-in-running-mate-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
