      <title>欧盟警告匈牙利不要为俄罗斯人提供简化签证计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/eu-warns-hungary-over-simplified-visa-scheme-for-russians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，需要确定匈牙利放宽俄罗斯和白俄罗斯人工作签证规定的决定是否违反了欧盟对俄罗斯的制裁并危及俄罗斯的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/eu-warns-hungary-over-simplified-visa-scheme-for-russians</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 08:37:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
